    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Ignursos wield enough strength to punch through rock, and even after death, their claws ignite with momentary heat when struck against another surface. Weaponsmiths can stabilize the claws&rsquo; supernatural ignition and incorporate them into bladed gauntlets known as ignurso knuckles. These gauntlets&rsquo; ignurso-hide coverings protect the wielder from the claws&rsquo; heat, and high-end models allow the claws to retract into wrist sheathes.</p>"
